Its just a simple dfs on the tree. They ask you to do the pre-order traversal. So first we add the element to the list then traversal the left sub tree and then right sub tree.

## Type of Traversal

Inorder    -> left , current , right
Pre-order  -> current , left , right
Post order -> left , right , current

Left means traversal the left sub tree.
Right means traversal the right sub tree.
Current means we need to do the process for the current node. Here we simiply added into the list.

