# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
1. Start off with two-pointers (start and end).
2. Create a loop with breaking conditions i.e left must be less than right.
3. Swap the values with each other in each iteration.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
