to check for repeated element `Y` we simply modify array as we visit number i we modify the element at ith index so if we visit again we will know.
for missing element `y` we calculate `(1 ^ 2 ^ 3 ^  . . .  ^ x ^ y^  . . .  ^n)` ^ `(nums[0] ^ nums[1] ^ . . .  ^ y ^ y ^  . . .  ^ nums[n])` that wiil be equal to `x ^ y`.
