Weight of all the entries created in the Trie from this word will carry a weight of 0 as they originate from word at 0th index of words.
Two inner for loops:
i=0, j=0 to j=2 * 5-2, so the Trie entry created is **test{test**
i=1, j=1 to j=2 * 5-2, so the Trie entry created is **est{test**
